<ab facs="#facs_269_r1l15">mıt Jm <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / do ward von ſeinr <expan>wırtin<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> getan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_269_r1l16">daʒ er auf dıſʒ ʒeıt nıht anheim bey vns <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> . Doch wenn er <expan>h<ex>er</ex>heim</expan> </ab>
